documentation.summary:
Use the Apigee API to programmatically develop and manage APIs
with a set of RESTful operations. Develop and secure API proxies,
deploy and undeploy API proxy revisions, monitor APIs, configure
environments, manage users, and more.

Note: This product is available as a free trial
for a time period of 60 days.
